data.description: Clean and well maintained ranch style home built in 2021 in the newer built community of Live Oak Creek with quiet and scenic surroundings. The home sits on a large lot and backs to a green belt with panoramic views of the gorgeous Texas sunrise and the beautiful Fort Worth skyline. The home has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with large open floor plan and granite counter tops and a sleep kitchen design.  The primary bedroom has large bay windows with a great view and a great bathroom suite with dual sinks and a large walk in closet.  Other bedrooms are good size and on other side of the home.  The backyard is a premier lot in the neighborhood.  Customized oversized covered patio with great views.  Backyard has room for a pool or other activities too.  Garage is equipped with a 220 volt outlet for electric vehicles if needed.  FHA assumable with 3.375% rate!!
